{"tid":2159274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"入去支持下NBA細路MatanEven嘅訪問","createTime":"2020-08-16T08:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T08:42:52.000Z","uid":344803,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a433e45e0f223b4baa0c702d7323cf197d95e8ac","tid":2159274,"uid":344803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jt2i2CEzBSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJt2i2CEzBSo&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=7db2281b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jt2i2CEzBSo</a><br />\nMatan Even full interview with Owen Shroyer<br />\n<br />\n13歲國際線手足Matan自從喺NBA直播show件Free HK嘅t shirt出黎，一直keep住有喺YouTube po關於香港警暴嘅片。但YouTube受中共影響，成日demonitize甚至remove佢啲片，導致冇乜人睇到。<br />\n<br />\n今次條片唔係警暴片，係佢接受INFO WARS嘅訪問片段，請入去支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年紀細細做咁多嘢幫助其他地方嘅民主自由真係好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，佢有新片我會po喺呢個po度：<br />\nNBA細路MatanEven有嘢同手足講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/apNmtFU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/apNmtFU</a><br />\n要記得定期去cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e401632ea45c53002310067308e96ee80406c695","tid":2159274,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n國際戰線要人<br />\nTwitter 要人呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b336780178543a2d1e806ad6e975cec52ee0441","tid":2159274,"uid":344803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"p牌自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3181f6658626204d5b7550baebee7976131833e5","tid":2159274,"uid":339330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{